OL,3,CMan in his 30s dies after being
OL,4,Cstabbed in Crystal Palace
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after a man was stabbed in
OL,8,Fsouth-east London.
OL,10,FPolice were called to Westow Hill,
OL,11,FCrystal Palace, at 3.39am on Sunday by
OL,12,Fthe London Ambulance Service after
OL,13,Freports of a stabbing.
OL,15,FOfficers found a 30-year-old seriously
OL,16,Finjured man who was treated at the
OL,17,Fscene and is now in hospital, the
OL,18,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
