OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782132502
OL,3,CMan in his 30s dies after being
OL,4,Cstabbed in Crystal Palace
OL,6,FSoon afterwards, police found another
OL,7,Fman, who is believed to be in his 30s,
OL,8,Fin the Westow Hill area with stab
OL,9,Fwounds.
OL,11,FHe later died at the scene.
OL,13,FThe man in hospital, whose injuries
OL,14,Fare described as neither life-
OL,15,Fthreatening nor life-changing, has now
OL,16,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of murder.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
