OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782132502
OL,3,CMan in his 30s dies after being
OL,4,Cstabbed in Crystal Palace
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Sarah Lee,
OL,7,Fwho is leading the investigation,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our officers responded quickly
OL,9,Falongside the London Ambulance Service
OL,10,Fwho did everything possible to help
OL,11,Fthe victim.
OL,13,F"This is a fast-moving investigation
OL,14,Fand residents in Crystal Palace will
OL,15,Fcontinue to notice an extensive police
OL,16,Fpresence today as our inquiries
OL,17,Fcontinue."
